{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.1","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 4:1","prev_osis_id":"Lev.003.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.004.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Les sacrifices d\u2019expiation<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-12: cf. (H\u00e9 5:1-3; 7:26-28.) L\u00e9 16:3, 11-14.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.4.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>L\u2019\u00c9ternel parla \u00e0 Mo\u00efse, et dit:<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.4","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.2","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:2","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.3.17","name":"L\u00e9vitique 3:17","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.3.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.2","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 4:2","prev_osis_id":"Lev.004.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.004.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.4.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Parle aux enfants d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, et dis: Lorsque quelqu\u2019un p\u00e9chera involontairement contre l\u2019un des commandements de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, en faisant des choses qui ne doivent point se faire;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.4","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.3","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:3","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.1","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:1","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.3","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 4:3","prev_osis_id":"Lev.004.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.004.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.4.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Si c\u2019est le sacrificateur ayant re\u00e7u l\u2019onction qui a p\u00e9ch\u00e9 et a rendu par l\u00e0 le peuple coupable, il offrira \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel, pour le p\u00e9ch\u00e9 qu\u2019il a commis, un jeune taureau sans d\u00e9faut, en sacrifice d\u2019expiation.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.4","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.4","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:4","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.2","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:2","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.4","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 4:4","prev_osis_id":"Lev.004.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.004.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.4.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Il am\u00e8nera le taureau \u00e0 l\u2019entr\u00e9e de la tente d\u2019assignation, devant l\u2019\u00c9ternel; et il posera sa main sur la t\u00eate du taureau, qu\u2019il \u00e9gorgera devant l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.4","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.5","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:5","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.3","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:3","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.5","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 4:5","prev_osis_id":"Lev.004.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.004.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.4.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Le sacrificateur ayant re\u00e7u l\u2019onction prendra du sang du taureau, et l\u2019apportera dans la tente d\u2019assignation;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.4","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.6","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:6","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.4","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:4","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.6","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 4:6","prev_osis_id":"Lev.004.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.004.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.4.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>il trempera son doigt dans le sang, et il en fera sept fois l\u2019aspersion devant l\u2019\u00c9ternel, en face du voile du sanctuaire.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.4","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.7","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:7","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.5","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:5","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.7","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 4:7","prev_osis_id":"Lev.004.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.004.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.4.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Le sacrificateur mettra du sang sur les cornes de l\u2019autel des parfums odorif\u00e9rants, qui est devant l\u2019\u00c9ternel dans la tente d\u2019assignation; et il r\u00e9pandra tout le sang du taureau au pied de l\u2019autel des holocaustes, qui est \u00e0 l\u2019entr\u00e9e de la tente d\u2019assignation.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.4","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.8","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:8","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.6","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:6","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.8","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 4:8","prev_osis_id":"Lev.004.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.004.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.4.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Il enl\u00e8vera toute la graisse du taureau expiatoire, la graisse qui couvre les entrailles et toute celle qui y est attach\u00e9e,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.4","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.9","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:9","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.7","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:7","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.9","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 4:9","prev_osis_id":"Lev.004.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.004.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.4.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>les deux rognons, et la graisse qui les entoure, qui couvre les flancs, et le grand lobe du foie, qu\u2019il d\u00e9tachera pr\u00e8s des rognons.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.4","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.10","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:10","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.8","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:8","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.10","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 4:10","prev_osis_id":"Lev.004.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.004.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.4.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Le sacrificateur enl\u00e8vera ces parties comme on les enl\u00e8ve du taureau dans le sacrifice d\u2019actions de gr\u00e2ces, et il les br\u00fblera sur l\u2019autel des holocaustes.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.4","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.11","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:11","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.9","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:9","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.11","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 4:11","prev_osis_id":"Lev.004.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.004.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.4.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Mais la peau du taureau, toute sa chair, avec sa t\u00eate, ses jambes, ses entrailles et ses excr\u00e9ments,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.4","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.12","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:12","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.10","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:10","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.12","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 4:12","prev_osis_id":"Lev.004.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.004.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.4.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>le taureau entier, il l\u2019emportera hors du camp, dans un lieu pur, o\u00f9 l\u2019on jette les cendres, et il le br\u00fblera au feu sur du bois: c\u2019est sur le tas de cendres qu\u2019il sera br\u00fbl\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.4","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.13","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:13","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.11","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:11","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.13","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 4:13","prev_osis_id":"Lev.004.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.004.014,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 13-21: cf. No 15:22-26. 2 Ch 29:20-24.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.4.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Si c\u2019est toute l\u2019assembl\u00e9e d\u2019Isra\u00ebl qui a p\u00e9ch\u00e9 involontairement et sans s\u2019en apercevoir, en faisant contre l\u2019un des commandements de l\u2019\u00c9ternel des choses qui ne doivent point se faire et en se rendant ainsi coupable,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.4","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.14","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.12","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:12","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.14","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 4:14","prev_osis_id":"Lev.004.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.004.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.4.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>et que le p\u00e9ch\u00e9 qu\u2019on a commis vienne \u00e0 \u00eatre d\u00e9couvert, l\u2019assembl\u00e9e offrira un jeune taureau en sacrifice d\u2019expiation, et on l\u2019am\u00e8nera devant la tente d\u2019assignation.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.4","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.15","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:15","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.13","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:13","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.15","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 4:15","prev_osis_id":"Lev.004.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.004.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.4.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Les anciens d\u2019Isra\u00ebl poseront leurs mains sur la t\u00eate du taureau devant l\u2019\u00c9ternel, et on \u00e9gorgera le taureau devant l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.4","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.16","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:16","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.14","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.16","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 4:16","prev_osis_id":"Lev.004.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.004.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.4.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Le sacrificateur ayant re\u00e7u l\u2019onction apportera du sang du taureau dans la tente d\u2019assignation;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.4","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.17","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:17","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.15","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:15","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.17","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 4:17","prev_osis_id":"Lev.004.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.004.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.4.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>il trempera son doigt dans le sang, et il en fera sept fois l\u2019aspersion devant l\u2019\u00c9ternel, en face du voile.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.4","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.18","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:18","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.16","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:16","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.18","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 4:18","prev_osis_id":"Lev.004.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.004.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.4.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Il mettra du sang sur les cornes de l\u2019autel qui est devant l\u2019\u00c9ternel dans la tente d\u2019assignation; et il r\u00e9pandra tout le sang au pied de l\u2019autel des holocaustes, qui est \u00e0 l\u2019entr\u00e9e de la tente d\u2019assignation.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.4","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.19","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:19","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.17","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:17","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.19","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 4:19","prev_osis_id":"Lev.004.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.004.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.4.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>Il enl\u00e8vera toute la graisse du taureau, et il la br\u00fblera sur l\u2019autel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.4","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.20","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:20","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.18","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:18","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.20","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 4:20","prev_osis_id":"Lev.004.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.004.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.4.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>Il fera de ce taureau comme du taureau expiatoire; il fera de m\u00eame. C\u2019est ainsi que le sacrificateur fera pour eux l\u2019expiation, et il leur sera pardonn\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.4","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.21","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:21","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.19","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:19","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.21","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 4:21","prev_osis_id":"Lev.004.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.004.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.4.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>Il emportera le taureau hors du camp, et il le br\u00fblera comme le premier taureau. C\u2019est un sacrifice d\u2019expiation pour l\u2019assembl\u00e9e.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.4","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.22","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:22","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.20","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:20","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.22","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 4:22","prev_osis_id":"Lev.004.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.004.023,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 22-35: cf. No 15:27-31. L\u00e9 5:1-13.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.4.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>Si c\u2019est un chef qui a p\u00e9ch\u00e9, en faisant involontairement contre l\u2019un des commandements de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, son Dieu, des choses qui ne doivent point se faire et en se rendant ainsi coupable,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.4","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.23","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:23","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.21","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:21","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.23","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 4:23","prev_osis_id":"Lev.004.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.004.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.4.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>et qu\u2019il vienne \u00e0 d\u00e9couvrir le p\u00e9ch\u00e9 qu\u2019il a commis, il offrira en sacrifice un bouc m\u00e2le sans d\u00e9faut.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.4","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.24","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:24","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.22","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:22","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.24","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 4:24","prev_osis_id":"Lev.004.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.004.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.4.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>Il posera sa main sur la t\u00eate du bouc, qu\u2019il \u00e9gorgera dans le lieu o\u00f9 l\u2019on \u00e9gorge les holocaustes devant l\u2019\u00c9ternel. C\u2019est un sacrifice d\u2019expiation.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.4","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.25","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:25","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.23","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:23","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.25","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 4:25","prev_osis_id":"Lev.004.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.004.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.4.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>Le sacrificateur prendra avec son doigt du sang de la victime expiatoire, il en mettra sur les cornes de l\u2019autel des holocaustes, et il r\u00e9pandra le sang au pied de l\u2019autel des holocaustes.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.4","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.26","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:26","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.24","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:24","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.26","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 4:26","prev_osis_id":"Lev.004.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.004.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.4.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>Il br\u00fblera toute la graisse sur l\u2019autel, comme la graisse du sacrifice d\u2019actions de gr\u00e2ces. C\u2019est ainsi que le sacrificateur fera pour ce chef l\u2019expiation de son p\u00e9ch\u00e9, et il lui sera pardonn\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.4","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.27","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:27","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.25","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:25","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.27","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 4:27","prev_osis_id":"Lev.004.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.004.028,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.4.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>Si c\u2019est quelqu\u2019un du peuple qui a p\u00e9ch\u00e9 involontairement, en faisant contre l\u2019un des commandements de l\u2019\u00c9ternel des choses qui ne doivent point se faire et en se rendant ainsi coupable,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.4","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.28","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:28","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.26","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:26","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.28","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 4:28","prev_osis_id":"Lev.004.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.004.029,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.4.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup>et qu\u2019il vienne \u00e0 d\u00e9couvrir le p\u00e9ch\u00e9 qu\u2019il a commis, il offrira en sacrifice une ch\u00e8vre, une femelle sans d\u00e9faut, pour le p\u00e9ch\u00e9 qu\u2019il a commis.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.4","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.29","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:29","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.29"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.27","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:27","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"29","lastverse":"29","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.29","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.29","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 4:29","prev_osis_id":"Lev.004.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.004.030,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.4.29\" class=\"v\">29<\/sup>Il posera sa main sur la t\u00eate de la victime expiatoire, qu\u2019il \u00e9gorgera dans le lieu o\u00f9 l\u2019on \u00e9gorge les holocaustes.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.4","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.30","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:30","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.30"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.28","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:28","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.28"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"30","lastverse":"30","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.30","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.30","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 4:30","prev_osis_id":"Lev.004.029,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.004.031,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.4.30\" class=\"v\">30<\/sup>Le sacrificateur prendra avec son doigt du sang de la victime, il en mettra sur les cornes de l\u2019autel des holocaustes, et il r\u00e9pandra tout le sang au pied de l\u2019autel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.4","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.31","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:31","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.31"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.29","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:29","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.29"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"31","lastverse":"31","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.31","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.31","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 4:31","prev_osis_id":"Lev.004.030,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.004.032,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.4.31\" class=\"v\">31<\/sup>Le sacrificateur \u00f4tera toute la graisse, comme on \u00f4te la graisse du sacrifice d\u2019actions de gr\u00e2ces, et il la br\u00fblera sur l\u2019autel, et elle sera d\u2019une agr\u00e9able odeur \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel. C\u2019est ainsi que le sacrificateur fera pour cet homme l\u2019expiation, et il lui sera pardonn\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.4","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.32","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:32","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.32"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.30","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:30","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.30"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"32","lastverse":"32","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.32","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.32","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 4:32","prev_osis_id":"Lev.004.031,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.004.033,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.4.32\" class=\"v\">32<\/sup>S\u2019il offre un agneau en sacrifice d\u2019expiation, il offrira une femelle sans d\u00e9faut.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.4","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.33","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:33","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.33"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.31","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:31","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.31"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"33","lastverse":"33","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.33","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.33","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 4:33","prev_osis_id":"Lev.004.032,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.004.034,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.4.33\" class=\"v\">33<\/sup>Il posera sa main sur la t\u00eate de la victime, qu\u2019il \u00e9gorgera en sacrifice d\u2019expiation dans le lieu o\u00f9 l\u2019on \u00e9gorge les holocaustes.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.4","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.34","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:34","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.34"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.32","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:32","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.32"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"34","lastverse":"34","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.34","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.34","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 4:34","prev_osis_id":"Lev.004.033,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.004.035,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.4.34\" class=\"v\">34<\/sup>Le sacrificateur prendra avec son doigt du sang de la victime, il en mettra sur les cornes de l\u2019autel des holocaustes, et il r\u00e9pandra tout le sang au pied de l\u2019autel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.4","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.35","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:35","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.35"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.33","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:33","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.33"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"35","lastverse":"35","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.35","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.35","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 4:35","prev_osis_id":"Lev.004.034,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.005.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.4.35\" class=\"v\">35<\/sup>Le sacrificateur \u00f4tera toute la graisse, comme on \u00f4te la graisse de l\u2019agneau dans le sacrifice d\u2019actions de gr\u00e2ces, et il la br\u00fblera sur l\u2019autel, comme un sacrifice consum\u00e9 par le feu devant l\u2019\u00c9ternel. C\u2019est ainsi que le sacrificateur fera pour cet homme l\u2019expiation du p\u00e9ch\u00e9 qu\u2019il a commis, et il lui sera pardonn\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.4","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.5.1","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5:1","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.34","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:34","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.34"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81f16843b07.30833484');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81f16843b07.30833484\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81f16843b07.30833484","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81f16843b07.30833484'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81f16843b07.30833484\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}